highlights.text: “Mr. John Deere” by Knivblad is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Norway at #3.
Sabrina Carpenter has the most spots on Viral Songs Norway. “Tears” is the highest at #38.
“No Broke Boys” by Disco Lines and Tinashe has been on Viral Songs Norway the longest, at 85 days straight.
“Her Name Was Fire” by Samuel Cabana is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Norway, up 13 spots at #7.
